        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="indent(3)"><placeName>New York</placeName>, <date>Feb. 14th. 5611</date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Sir;</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">I am instructed by the Board of<lb/> Trustees of the Congregation
                B'ne Jeshurun, to<lb/> inform you, that the ceremony of laying the Founda-<lb/>tion
                Stone of their new Synagogue will take place<lb/> on <date>Tuesday, the 25th</date>
                inst. at 2 o'clock, P. M.<lb/> on which occasion the honor of your company is<lb/>
                earnestly solicited. For particulars see the accom-<lb/> panying Ordre of
                Service.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I am, Sir,</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Yours most Respectfully;</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)"><persName role="author">HENRY GOLDSMITH</persName>, Sec'y. C. B.
                J.</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">_____________</p>
            <p>N. B. Should the weather not be propitious, the ceremony will<lb/> take place on the
                    <date>Tuesday</date> following.</p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
